    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/c4584c9c9a66cdc888723dea4de78ae7.webp?t=1745260861\" width=38 height=36 /></span><strong>【新增】从上次见面以来，我们做了什么？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢参与了上次新品节的各位玩家！基于大家的反馈，进行了以下优化：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更丝滑的难度曲线</strong>：重新编排了关卡顺序，让新手更轻松入门，老玩家也能找到新的挑战节奏！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由探索的非线性关卡</strong>：全新的关卡选择界面，带来清晰脉络的同时仍可自由跳转，重温喜爱的关卡。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望这次优化能带给喜爱推箱子游戏的你更流畅的解谜体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，真正的惊喜将留给即将面世的正式版！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/f1c2a2cf9cffae6c7154e5308392ceb2.webp?t=1745260861\" width=38 height=38 /></span><strong>【新增】正式版会有什么？抢先一瞥！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在正式版中，我们为“基于文字推箱子”注入了更多脑洞：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*为保留完整版的终极体验，下述机制暂未加入试玩版</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>箱子大变身：</strong><i>变，都可以变</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小家伙们：</strong><i>它们的特别之处不仅是外观，还有组合方式</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>识别与切分：</strong><i>你好，你被选中了，出来一下</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>倒计时告别：</strong><i>和生活一样，有些存在会逐步消失，无法挽留</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >立即将《Wordban》加入愿望单，见证瓦豆的完全成长！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【关于此游戏】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/46da6b629cf6d8cae47e19cf36f90831.webp?t=1745260861\" width=37 height=38 /></span>大家好！《Wordban》的免费试玩版来啦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Wordban》</strong>是一款基于文字的推箱子游戏。操控小可爱“<strong>瓦豆</strong>”推动箱子，触发各关卡创新的文字规则，改变箱子的布局、数量甚至属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/6f1136544dd2c6f256ec6ab55815c2b9.poster.avif?t=1745260861\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/6f1136544dd2c6f256ec6ab55815c2b9.webm?t=1745260861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/6f1136544dd2c6f256ec6ab55815c2b9.mp4?t=1745260861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/c4584c9c9a66cdc888723dea4de78ae7.webp?t=1745260861\" width=38 height=36 /></span>在你的策略下，瓦豆可以让箱子以少变多、合二为一、滴水穿石，甚至点石成金！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《Wordban Demo》</strong>中，你将可以提前免费体验到游戏的第一个大章节：<strong>房间/The Room</strong>，包含20个精心设计的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/004b772183ad2d21e6b6e064923e3438.poster.avif?t=1745260861\" width=800 height=528 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/004b772183ad2d21e6b6e064923e3438.webm?t=1745260861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/004b772183ad2d21e6b6e064923e3438.mp4?t=1745260861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202180/extras/f1c2a2cf9cffae6c7154e5308392ceb2.webp?t=1745260861\" width=38 height=38 /></span>唤醒瓦豆，一起来享受解谜的独特乐趣！</p>",
